<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>Purple Heart • purple hearts</xh5><p> <i>Purple Heart</i>—(U.S.) a military decoration for those wounded in action: Mason returned to Pasadena wearing a Bronze Star and a <u>Purple Heart</u>.</p><p> <i>purple hearts</i>—(Drug users) heart-shaped stimulant tablets, especially of amphetamine <i>(also: pink hearts): </i>They took more interest in life and stopped taking <u>purple hearts</u>.</p> </entry>
